description: The data provider, or admprovider is a command line tool application that serves as a configuration tool for the MALOS-vision daemon and as a message relay with the infrastructure. The data provider will establish the required connections to the infrastructure, authenticate and obtain the right configurations for the specific version of the device running the face software.
